{
  "sequence": [
    {
      "step": 1,
      "type": "plain_text",
      "subject": "Congrats on Acme's sustainability push, Jane",
      "body": "Hi Jane,\n\nI saw Acme Corp’s recent sustainability initiative – impressive move! As Director of Operations, I thought you might be interested in how our AI automation platform can further reduce waste and cut costs.\n\nWould you have 15 min next week to chat?\n\nBest,\nAlex (LeadCraft)"
    },
    {
      "step": 2,
      "type": "html",
      "subject": "How AI can boost Acme's green goals",
      "body": "<html><body><p>Hi Jane,</p><p>Congratulations on the new sustainability initiative! 🎉 At LeadCraft we’ve helped companies like <strong>Acme Corp</strong> achieve up to <em>20% reduction</em> in energy consumption through AI‑driven process optimization.</p><p>Would you like a quick demo to see the potential impact on your operations?</p><p>Best regards,<br/>Alex<br/>LeadCraft</p></body></html>"
    },
    {
      "step": 3,
      "type": "plain_text",
      "subject": "Follow‑up on AI for Acme’s operations",
      "body": "Hi Jane,\n\nJust circling back on my previous messages. I understand budgets are under review, but a short conversation could uncover quick wins that pay for themselves.\n\nLet me know a convenient time.\n\nThanks,\nAlex"
    },
    {
      "step": 4,
      "type": "html",
      "subject": "Last chance: AI‑driven cost savings for Acme",
      "body": "<html><body><p>Hi Jane,</p><p>I don’t want to miss the opportunity to help Acme achieve its sustainability and cost‑saving targets before the new fiscal year.</p><p>Are you available for a 10‑minute call this week?</p><p>Looking forward to connecting.<br/>Alex<br/>LeadCraft</p></body></html>"
    }
  ]
}"
    }
